<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f5f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }
        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .logo { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .logo span { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
        .logo .brand { color: #2e9e5e; }
        .logo .name { color: #374151; }
        h1 { font-size: 20px; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 16px; }
        p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 16px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #2e9e5e; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .btn:hover { background-color: #268a50; }
        .btn-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
        .url { word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="logo">
                <span class="brand">Conzent</span>
            </div>

            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>

            <p>Hi {{ user.first_name ?: user.username }},</p>

            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. Click the button below to set a new password:</p>

            <div class="btn-wrap">
                <a href="{{ reset_url }}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
            </div>

            <p>This link will expire in <strong>{{ expiry_minutes }} minutes</strong>.</p>

            <p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>

            <p class="url">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>{{ reset_url }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Conzent. Open Consent Infrastructure{% if tcf_enabled %} — IAB TCF v2.3{% endif %} — CMP ID {{ cmp_id }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
